ucto
------------------------------------------
Ucto tokenizes text files: it separates words from punctuation, and splits
sentences. It offers several other basic preprocessing steps such as changing
case that you can all use to make your text suited for further processing such
as indexing, part-of-speech tagging, or machine translation.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.6-1
  libexttextcat2.0_0-3.4.6-1bl1
  libfolia19-2.15-1bl1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libgomp1-11.3.0-1
  libicu72-72.1-1
  libreadline7-8.2-2
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  libticcutils9-0.32-1bl1
  libucto-devel-0.29-1bl1
  libucto6-0.29-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.5-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.40-1
  cygport-0.36.4-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libexttextcat2.0-devel-3.4.6-1bl1
  libfolia-devel-2.15-1bl1
  libicu-devel-72.1-1
  libreadline-devel-8.2-2
  libticcutils-devel-0.32-1bl1
  libtool-2.4.7-1
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  make-4.4.1-2
  uctodata-0.9.1-1bl1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/ucto

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/ucto/archive/refs/tags/v0.29.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ucto-0.29-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ucto-0.29-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ucto-0.29-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ucto-0.29-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libucto6-0.29-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libucto-devel-0.29-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ucto)
  /usr/bin/ucto.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ucto.README
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/MAINTAINERS
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/README
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/TODO
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/ucto_manual.pdf
  /usr/share/doc/ucto/ucto_manual.rst
  /usr/share/man/man1/ucto.1.gz
  /usr/share/ucto/textcat.cfg
  /usr/share/ucto/textcat_alt.cfg
  /usr/share/ucto/textcat_normal.cfg

(libucto6)
  /usr/bin/cygucto-6.dll

(libucto-devel)
  /usr/include/ucto/my_textcat.h
  /usr/include/ucto/setting.h
  /usr/include/ucto/tokenize.h
  /usr/lib/libucto.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ucto.pc

